{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b52fa28488","title":"在陈云关于经济形势和调整措施的报告稿中加写的两段话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"33912bb42f","index":0,"year":1950,"month":6,"day":11,"articleId":"b52fa28488"}],"tags":[{"id":"a2f6c6af57","name":"陈云","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"644f8f6af6","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b52fa28488","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是陈云准备向政协第一届全国委员会第二次会议所作的报告。这个报告后来作于1950年6月15日。"}],"contents":[{"id":"4fa15f0c43","type":"title","text":"在陈云关于经济形势和调整措施的报告稿中加写的两段话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b52fa28488"},{"id":"644f8f6af6","type":"paragraph","text":"有些人提议由政府制订投资条例或公司法，我们认为有此必要，现正在起草中","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b52fa28488"},{"id":"82f889bd66","type":"paragraph","text":"最近三个月来，中央劳动部召集了一次各省、市的劳动局长会议，政务院财经委员会召集了一次各大城市的工商局长会议，中央财政部召集了一次各大城市的税务局长会议，详尽地讨论了有关劳资关系、调整工商业和调整税收诸问题。这三次会议均有私人工商业代表参加。我现在报告的，大都是这些会议的共同意见和结论。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b52fa28488"}],"page":{"id":"e95563b3b3","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b52fa28488","start":470,"end":470}}}},"__N_SSG":true}